<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>New Submission from RateMyService White-Label Setup Page</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            background-color: #f4f4f4;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
        }
        .container {
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 20px auto;
            background-color: #ffffff;
            padding: 20px;
            border: 1px solid #dddddd;
            border-radius: 5px;
        }
        h2 {
            color: #333333;
        }
        table {
            width: 100%;
            border-collapse: collapse;
        }
        table th, table td {
            padding: 10px;
            border: 1px solid #dddddd;
            text-align: left;
        }
        table th {
            background-color: #f2f2f2;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>

<div class="container">
    <h2>New email submission from RateMyService White-Label Setup</h2>
    <p>Someone just submitted a White-Label application form on <a href="https://ratemyservice.io/white-label-application">https://ratemyservice.io/white-label-application</a> with the following message:</p>

    <table>
        <tr>
            <th>RateMyService Dashboard URL</th>
            <td>{{ sender.dashboardUrl }}</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
            <th>Company Name</th>
            <td>{{ sender.companyName }}</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
            <th>Email Address</th>
            <td>{{ sender.email }}</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
            <th>Purchased Codes</th>
            <td>{{ sender.codes }}</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
            <th>Domain Name</th>
            <td>{{ sender.domainName }}</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
            <th>Sub-Domain for White-Label</th>
            <td>{{ sender.subdomain }}</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
            <th>FROM and REPLY-TO Email Address</th>
            <td>{{ sender.fromEmail }}</td>
        </tr>
    </table>
</div>

</body>
</html>
